</taxonomicName>
, 
<emphasis id="F0B6CD32FFAC0806FC200FCEFBC469DF" bold="true" box="[954,1043,153,179]" pageId="7">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="EB857049FFAC0806FC200FCEFBC469DF" box="[954,1043,153,179]" pageId="7" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
belongs to the 
<taxonomicName id="05C26AA3FFAC0806FB260FCEFABF69DF" authorityName="Kerremans" authorityYear="1912" box="[1212,1384,153,179]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tricolor" subGenus="Merocratus">
<emphasis id="F0B6CD32FFAC0806FB260FCEFB1A69DF" box="[1212,1229,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="7">A</emphasis>
. (
<emphasis id="F0B6CD32FFAC0806FB7E0FCDFAD469DF" box="[1252,1283,154,179]" italics="true" pageId="7">M.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="F0B6CD32FFAC0806FA880FCEFABF69DF" box="[1298,1384,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="7">tricolor</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species-group and it resembles by the violet colouration and triangular body 
<taxonomicName id="05C26AA3FFAC0806FC550FEAFB4769BB" authorityName=": Bily" authorityYear="1999" box="[975,1168,189,215]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longipilis" subGenus="Merocratus">
<emphasis id="F0B6CD32FFAC0806FC550FEAFC3769BB" box="[975,992,189,215]" italics="true" pageId="7">A</emphasis>
. (
<emphasis id="F0B6CD32FFAC0806FC6D0FE9FBC169BB" box="[1015,1046,190,215]" italics="true" pageId="7">M.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="F0B6CD32FFAC0806FBBC0FEAFB4769BB" box="[1062,1168,189,215]" italics="true" pageId="7">longipilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and the male of 
<taxonomicName id="05C26AA3FFAC0806FAD60FEAFF0A6997" authority="Bílý &amp; Plachetka, 2019" authorityName="Bílý &amp; Plachetka" authorityYear="2019" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="priska" status="sp. nov." subGenus="Merocratus">
<emphasis id="F0B6CD32FFAC0806FAD60FEAFA8A69BB" box="[1356,1373,189,215]" italics="true" pageId="7">A</emphasis>
. (
<emphasis id="F0B6CD32FFAC0806FAEF0FE9FA4369BB" box="[1397,1428,190,215]" italics="true" pageId="7">M.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="F0B6CD32FFAC0806FF0D0FB6FF0A6997" box="[151,221,225,251]" italics="true" pageId="7">priska</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="F0B6CD32FFAC0806FF7E0FB6FEEA6997" bold="true" box="[228,317,225,251]" pageId="7">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="EB857049FFAC0806FF7E0FB6FEEA6997" box="[228,317,225,251]" pageId="7" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
From the former it differs by the entire asetose body and the shape of the male genitalia (
<figureCitation id="5AF90DA5FFAC0806FABF0FB6FAA16997" box="[1317,1398,225,251]" captionStart="FIGURES 10–15" captionStartId="4.[151,264,748,773]" captionTargetBox="[157,1429,174,724]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,166,729]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 10–15. Subgen. Merocratus (aedeagi, schematically, not in scale). 10—Anthaxia (M.) jakli Bílý, 1996, holotype; 11—A. (M.) miranda Deyrolle, 1864 (Kalimantan); 12—A. (M.) angustata sp. nov., Bílý, holotype; 13—A. (M.) priska Bílý, sp. nov., holotype; 14—A. (M.) violaceidorsis Bílý, sp. nov., holotype; 15—A. (M.) lucifera Plachetka, sp. nov., holotype." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3557863" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3557863/files/figure.png" pageId="7">Fig. 14</figureCitation>
vs. 
<figureCitation id="5AF90DA5FFAC0806FF0D0E52FF306873" box="[151,231,261,287]" captionStart="FIGURES 10–15" captionStartId="4.[151,264,748,773]" captionTargetBox="[157,1429,174,724]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,166,729]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 10–15. Subgen. Merocratus (aedeagi, schematically, not in scale). 10—Anthaxia (M.) jakli Bílý, 1996, holotype; 11—A. (M.) miranda Deyrolle, 1864 (Kalimantan); 12—A. (M.) angustata sp. nov., Bílý, holotype; 13—A. (M.) priska Bílý, sp. nov., holotype; 14—A. (M.) violaceidorsis Bílý, sp. nov., holotype; 15—A. (M.) lucifera Plachetka, sp. nov., holotype." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3557863" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3557863/files/figure.png" pageId="7">
Fig. 
<quantity id="053ABCC5FFAC0806FF510E52FF306873" box="[203,231,261,287]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.302" pageId="7" unit="in" value="13.0">13</quantity>
</figureCitation>
in 
<bibRefCitation id="A6536CD1FFAC0806FE970E52FE526873" author="Bily, S." box="[269,389,261,287]" pageId="7" pagination="125 - 146" refId="ref6191" refString="Bily, S. (1998) A revision of Anthaxia (subgen. Merocratus) (Coleoptera: Buprestidae). Folia Heyrovskyana, 6, 125 - 146." type="journal article" year="1998">Bílý, 1998</bibRefCitation>
) from latter it differs by the more strongly depressed frons, colouration of the pronotum and ventral surface and by the quite different shape of the male genitalia (
<figureCitation id="5AF90DA5FFAC0806FC3B0E7EFC2B682F" box="[929,1020,297,323]" captionStart="FIGURES 10–15" captionStartId="4.[151,264,748,773]" captionTargetBox="[157,1429,174,724]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,166,729]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 10–15. Subgen. Merocratus (aedeagi, schematically, not in scale). 10—Anthaxia (M.) jakli Bílý, 1996, holotype; 11—A. (M.) miranda Deyrolle, 1864 (Kalimantan); 12—A. (M.) angustata sp. nov., Bílý, holotype; 13—A. (M.) priska Bílý, sp. nov., holotype; 14—A. (M.) violaceidorsis Bílý, sp. nov., holotype; 15—A. (M.) lucifera Plachetka, sp. nov., holotype." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3557863" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3557863/files/figure.png" pageId="7">Figs. 14</figureCitation>
vs. 13).
</paragraph>
